//Left Ventricle - Function

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 06 of Cardio MRI

When I select 'Function' checkbox
Then 'Kinetic disorder' checkbox is enabled
And 'Mid-ventricular wall movement disorder' checkbox is enabled
And 'Apical Ballooning' checkbox is enabled
And 'Aneurysm' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Kinetic disorder' checkbox
Then 'Localization' is enabled

When I select 'Aneurysm' checkbox
Then 'Localization' dropdown menu is enabled